  context.arch.discoverer.query.AbstractQueryItem<C1,C2>

public abstract class RuleQueryItemND<C1,C2>
extends AbstractQueryItem<C1,C2>

QueryItem that can handle multiple dimensions (or attributes or element), rather than just one. Useful for cases such as calculating distance based on latitude and longitude, with a third attribute for error margin. TODO: rename to MultiQueryItem?
